title: She had a relationship with another man but now I see her in my dream, what to do?
transcript: Assalamu Alaikum Wa Rahmatullahi Wa Barakatu. Wa'alaykumussalam. There is a girl that ever approached to me several months ago. After that, she had a relationship with other woman. So I don't know and don't want to know about her anymore. That's not my question. It's her. But few years ago, she has appeared in my dream. And may you remember her again. What are you thinking about this matter according to your point of view? You need to be a man.
